About Us - pizzazznyc.com Home Menu About Us Catering Contact Order Now 38 Union Square East New York, New York 1003 +1 646 872 1187 info@pizzazz.com Home Menu About Us Catering Contact Order Now About Us Concept Who We Are? Pizzazz is our passion project—a place where we blend our love for great pizza and the hustle of NYC. This isn’t just pizza, it’s a piece of who we are. Pizzazz brings a fresh take on fast food with Neapolitan-inspired pizza, adding a New York twist. Every pizza is personal-sized, made from scratch, and fired up right when you order, combining traditional craftsmanship with bold flavors. Our philosophy is simple: great pizza, made with passion, for people who love pizza as much as we do.
We believe that the great pizza starts with great dough.
It's the foundation of everything we do, bringing that perfect balance of chew, crisp, and flavor. Using Italian 00 flour, sea salt, yeast, and water, we let time do the rest-allowing our dough to rise and develop its unique texture. It's not just a base, it's the heart of every Pizza we make. Testimonials What Our Guests say "Absolutely delicious and will definitely be coming back. The pizza dough is perfect, and the ingredients are fresh. Staff is friendly and welcoming. I highly recommend." Noelani Rodriguez "The pizza here is amazing, and the staff couldn’t be friendlier. The dough was just right—light, crispy, and absolutely perfect. The ingredients tasted so fresh and vibrant. I tried the spicy salami pizza, and it hit all the right notes, with a perfect balance of heat and sweetness. Great place for lunch or dinner!" Pat Dorian "We ordered pizzas from Pizzazz for a wine party, and they were absolutely fantastic! The crust was perfectly crispy, the toppings were fresh, and each bite was bursting with flavor. It paired beautifully with our selection of wines, making the night truly special. Highly recommend this place for anyone looking to elevate their pizza experience!" Mikkel Solbakken "I found this place by accident and I must say it’s the best pizza I’ve had a long time! It was so tasty. I had prosciutto di Parma pizza and it comes as a whole pizza not a slice! The staff were lovely, they opened recently and were all excited. Will definitely be coming back to try other options." Bonnie Bon Founded in 2024, Pizzazz is dedicated to all pizza lovers. We invite you to join us on a journey where Neapolitan-inspired pizzas meet creative twist.
